item.title: SoftLayer_Account_Attribute_Type
item.description: SoftLayer_Account_Attribute_Type Datatype Description SoftLayer_Account_Attribute_Type models the type of attribute that can be assigned to a SoftLayer customer account. Local description A brief description of a SoftLayer account attribute type. Type: string id A SoftLayer account attribute type's internal identifier. Type: integer keyName A SoftLayer account attribute type's key name. This is typically a shorter version of an attribute type's name.
